text.__SUMMARY__:
Millettia warneckei is a species of legume in the family Fabaceae.
It is found in Ghana, Guinea, Liberia, Sierra Leone, and Togo.
It is threatened by habitat loss.
text.Sources: Hawthorne, W. (1998). "Millettia warneckei". The IUCN Red List of Threatened Species. IUCN. 1998: e.T34805A9889434. doi:10.2305/IUCN.UK.1998.RLTS.T34805A9889434.en. Retrieved 19 December 2017.
